{"tid":2326091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青提「聖誕」：X你老母","createTime":"2020-12-15T05:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T00:34:40.000Z","uid":26602,"like":178,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d08a193cf62f5b04639768d25199e1f2f9d0ba44","tid":2326091,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20121218/large/1355814467_b68d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20121218%2Flarge%2F1355814467_b68d.jpg&h=05bd91ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃，聊表心意，不過中原地產創辦人施永青對「聖誕」就有HardFeeling，《壹週刊》報道，施永青一聽到「聖誕」無名火起：「我最憎就是聖誕！」，細個因為屋企窮，無錢買聖誕卡買，所以他將人哋送畀佢張聖誕卡，改咗自己個名送畀人，點知同學將件事唱通街，超慘！仲話，「我已經同佢反左面架喇！」<br />\n<br />\n依家施永青財力雄厚，想送幾多果籃塞住人哋把口都得啦！佢話雖然收大把果籃，但一個都唔會送出去，仲好激動咁話，「你咪唔好同我做生意囉，笨！我X你老母」嚇到個記者打咗個突，童年的影響之大，真係唔講得笑！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20121218/Q5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2FQ5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=2ea540ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20121218%2FQ5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA%2F&h=1b25dbf9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20121218/Q5DKDPEDYJLW74W2JEL5ABU6BA/</a>"},{"pid":"37f61e5311f72ac6b51f11eb7158da1d77de27f6","tid":2326091,"uid":288801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d08a193cf62f5b04639768d25199e1f2f9d0ba44","tid":2326091,"uid":26602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20121218/large/1355814467_b68d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20121218%2Flarge%2F1355814467_b68d.jpg&h=05bd91ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖誕前各公司互送聖誕卡、果籃